705229f-a.text:
Eing's Highway, south side, near Nostrand Ave. This house
ing in 1936, would be in 31st Street, just north of Flatbush Ave.
1922.

705230f-b.title: Brooklyn: Kings Highway - Nostrand Avenue
705230f-b.text:
Kings Highway, south side, east of Nostrand Ave., and on line of
Eas. 31st Street, showing the John L. Bergen house built in 1875. (John
L. Bergen was born in 1835, married Anna, the daughter of Peter Lott in
1872 and died in 1880). This house was demolished in 1925.
1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
